properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! Wolves have been causing chaos in the village, attacking livestock and endangering the lives of innocent people. Brave heroes have been called upon to put an end to this threat. You must venture into the dense forests where the wolves reside and hunt them down. But be warned, these wolves are cunning and fierce, and will stop at nothing to protect their territory. Will you be able to rid the village of this danger and restore peace to the land?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}, did you hear about the corruption? Some animals are behaving aggressively since a fireball hit the forest near our village, a few days ago.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}! Feel free to browse my goods! I sell weapons and basic survival equipments.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hmm, I heard some really strange noises coming from downstairs today. Maybe the dead have something to say?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}, I cannot talk. I have some concerning news to the mayor, regarding our graveyard.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}. I'm {{npc.name}}! Nice to meet you! My father went to the frozen island yesterday, but didn't come back so far. I'm starting to get worried!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Watch out! This region of the city is known for having some bandits waiting to rob you!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Be careful while going south! A few goblins were spotted. These devilish creatures don't hesitate in throwing stones in whoever appears in front of them.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: We trapped this beast after a trip to the forest. It can easily kill an army alone!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! Are you going to Rivenn Island? I have some food sell. Feel free to browse my goods.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: {{char.name}}, want to visit the frozen island? Just go on the ship! Beware, this place is full of danger and creatures ready to kill you at anytime. Don't go if you're just starting your journey. I heard many adventures died recentlyr due to an Yeti attack.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! I'm just coming back from my expedition to the abandoned mines. You can follow this path to the right to get there... but be careful. I saw many bodies over there. Some creepy spiders are waiting for any mistake to attack.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hello {{char.name}}, how are you doing? My name is John and I’m a trader. I’ve been traveling the roads for over 15 years now, buying and selling goods from town to town. I’ve seen a lot of interesting places and met some fascinating people along the way. I’ve got some great items for sale, so if you’re looking for something special, be sure to take a look at my wares. Thanks for stopping by!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, careful when going beyond the city walls. I heard Orcs are settling nearby, planning a raid soon. Last time they burned the whole village down and we had to re-build what's left. These damn pigs!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Ah, welcome to my tavern, dearie! My name is Isabella, and I am the mistress of this fine establishment. What brings you in today? Are you looking for a cozy spot to warm yourself by the fire, or perhaps a refreshing ale to quench your thirst?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! Be careful with the Orcs, they can be very strong...

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to my forge, {{char.name}}. My name is Thorne Forgehammer, and I am the master blacksmith in these parts. What can I do for you today? Do you seek a sturdy sword to cleave through your enemies, a suit of armor to protect you from their blows, or perhaps some training equipment to hone your skills?

All of my wares are crafted with the finest materials and techniques, and I take great pride in the quality of my work. I am also skilled at repairs, so if your gear is in need of fixing, I am happy to take a look.

Take your time browsing my wares, and let me know if you have any questions or special requests. It would be my pleasure to assist you in your quest.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to our mystical emporium, {{char.name}}! How may we assist you on your journey today? Are you in need of potent potions, powerful runes, or perhaps a new staff to aid in your magical endeavors?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to my humble food stall, traveler! My name is Marisol, and I specialize in delicious street food that will satisfy your hunger on your journey. I have a variety of dishes to choose from, including savory meat pies, spicy kebabs, and sweet pastries.

All of my ingredients are fresh and locally sourced, and I take great pride in preparing each dish to perfection. If you're in a hurry, I have some pre-made meals ready to go, but if you have a little time to spare, I can prepare something fresh just for you.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to my shop, {{char.name}}! My name is Aiden, and I am a marksman specializing in ranged weapons. I offer a wide selection of weapons to suit your needs, including bows, arrows, slingshots, and more.

If you are in need of a new weapon, I highly recommend taking a look at my bows. Each bow is crafted with care and precision, using only the finest materials. And if you need ammunition, I have a variety of arrows and stones to choose from, including iron-tipped arrows for added piercing power.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey my son, how are you doing? Your father just left to the sewers because it seems they're having an emergency there with rat infestations. Could you help him with it? He carved a slingshot during his trip to the forest yesterday, and he said he want to give it to you.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to our bank! My name is Elara, and I am one of our bankers here. We offer a variety of financial services, including secure storage for your precious items, account management, loans, and investments.

If you need a safe place to store your valuable items or gold, we have a variety of storage options to suit your needs. We take great care in ensuring the security of our vaults, so you can rest assured that your items are safe with us.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
My name is Edmund, and I am one of the guards here at the bank. My job is to keep the bank and its customers safe, so if you see anything suspicious or have any concerns, don't hesitate to let me know.

We take the security of the bank and its customers very seriously, and have implemented a number of measures to ensure the safety of everyone inside. We have guards stationed at every entrance and exit, as well as security measures such as traps and alarms to deter would-be thieves.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to my blacksmith shop, {{char.name}}. I'm Grim Steelbender, and I've been forging weapons and armor for as long as I can remember. What brings you to my humble abode?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Ahoy, mate! Ye be lookin' to set sail for Asterion Island, eh? Well, I do have a boat for ye, but let me tell ye, that island is no place for the faint of heart.

There be minotaurs and cyclops on that land, and they be fierce creatures. They'll tear ye apart if ye ain't prepared. But if ye still want to go, I'll give ye some advice.

Cyclops got hides thicker than a whale's blubber. Most weapons won't do much damage to 'em. But if ye got a skilled archer in your crew, they might be able to hit their weak spots.

But let me warn ye again, mate. That island is a dangerous place, and them creatures ain't to be trifled with. So make sure ye and yer crew are ready for a fight before ye set foot on that land. And may the sea goddess bless ye on yer journey.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to my training shop. I am Master Bladewind, and I will be your instructor. Here, we do not simply learn how to wield a sword or fight. We learn how to master our bodies, our minds, and our spirits. We learn how to become true warriors.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to my shop, my friend. I am Rhys the Herbalist, and I am here to help you find whatever herbs or remedies you may need. How can I be of service to you today?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hello there, and welcome to my jewelry shop. My name is Olivia Green, and I am the owner. It's so lovely to have you here. What can I help you with today?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Halt! I am Sir Gareth of the Sacred Grove, sworn to protect this holy site from all who would profane it. This is a holy place, and it is not to be taken lightly. Show the proper respect and reverence at all times, and do not stray from the designated paths. 

Welcome to the shrine, traveler. May your stay here be peaceful and enlightening.

properties.name: name
properties.value: Sir Gareth of the Sacred Grove

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Halt! I am Darian Stormblade, the guardian of these training grounds. What brings you to this place? Are you here to test your mettle or seeking something else?

State your business before entering the training grounds. We don't allow just anyone to wander in.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Greetings, traveler! My singular eye gazes upon distant lands. Name thy destination, and I shall grant thee passage with a blink.
